# Goal: Enhance Grade 10 Accounting GAAP Topic

The objective is to align the Grade 10 Accounting principles (GAAP) topic with the recent UI and functionality enhancements implemented in the Ethics, Final Accounts, and Sole Trader modules. This involves updating the UI to display "GAAP" on selection cards, implementing the comprehensive hint and memo system, upgrading the practice mode to an 8-question timed review flow, and enriching the generator with content from the curriculum document.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> Please review the proposed subskills for the generator. Currently, the generator has `intro`, `principles`, and `matching_activity`. I plan to keep these logical groupings but expand their pools and ensure `matching_activity` directly uses the "Activity 1" from the curriculum document as a `table_wordbank` interactive activity. Let me know if you would like me to structure these subskills differently.

